</td>
<td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:39%; padding:0in 7px 0in 7px; height:46px; background-color:#e7e6e6; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none">
<p><span style="page:WordSection1"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:Palatino"><span style="color:black">Skin plaques with atypical CD4+ cells</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p> </p>
<p align="center" style="text-align:center"><span style="page:WordSection1"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:Palatino"><span style="color:black">May progress to Sezary syndrome aka T cell leukemia</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:37%; padding:0in 7px 0in 7px; height:46px; background-color:#e7e6e6; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none">
<p><span style="page:WordSection1"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:Palatino"><span style="color:black">Workup: Skin biopsy</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p> </p>
<p><span style="page:WordSection1"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:Palatino"><span style="color:black">Treatment: </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p><span style="page:WordSection1"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:Palatino"><span style="color:black">Light therapy, topical steroids, superficial radiation</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
