<td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:69px; padding:0in 7px 0in 7px; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black">
<p align="center" style="border:none; text-align:center"><span style="page:WordSection2"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><b><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:Palatino"><span style="color:black">Anaplastic Large Cell  Lymphoma (ALCL) </span></span></span></b></span></span></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:171px; padding:0in 7px 0in 7px; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top">
<p><span style="page:WordSection2"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:Palatino"><span style="color:black">&lt; 2% of NHL</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p style="border:none; margin-right:4px"><span style="page:WordSection2"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:Palatino"><span style="color:black">Primary cutaneous variant can arise from existing mycosis fungoides<br/>
			Worse outcome predictor includes increased </span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif"><span style="color:black">β</span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:Palatino"><span style="color:black">-2 microglobulin &gt;3  </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p style="border:none; margin-right:4px"><span style="page:WordSection2"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:Palatino"><span style="color:black">and age &gt;40 </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:108px; padding:0in 7px 0in 7px; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top">
